room_title: Escape room "Do Not Disturb" by Breakout Games - Baltimore in Baltimore
review: I love it here! I’ve done Do Not Disturb, Casino, and The Kidnapping and I’ve successfully made it out each time with our group! The staff is awesome and the rooms are challenging. I can’t wait to complete the rest of the rooms. Highly recommend for groups of 4+! Perfect rainy day activity and sometimes you can catch a good deal on Groupon!! Everyone must try an escape room at least once, they’re a lot of fun even if you aren’t great at puzzle solving!
